{"tid":2054394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共'18個不准'內部文件","createTime":"2020-06-07T06:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T13:04:43.000Z","uid":26770,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"dc28f56f6ef7bcf5dc308a3962e23f1cf74ad690","tid":2054394,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:39:23.000Z","msg":"9000萬黨員成奴隸<br />\n大陸網友傳：習共黨中央和國務院機關發布文件，一連規定18個&ldquo;不准&rdquo;。規定在&ldquo;任何場合&rdquo;&mdash;&mdash;&ldquo;任何&rdquo;二字表明包括一切私生活場合，不准說不同意見。特別點明&ldquo;不准發表偏離｛兩個維護｝的言論；不准點贊；不准瀏覽&ldquo;反動網站&rdquo;；不准&ldquo;收聽收看境外反動電台和電視節目&hellip;&hellip;全黨必須成政治殭屍<br />\n<br />\n共產黨的愚蠢就在於，這些條條框框是管不住人的，人是有私慾的。<br />\n<br />\n這些信息倒是讓黨外人士看到，共產黨今天內部已經混亂到了什麼程度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KEbCU9n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKEbCU9n.jpg&h=68905e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GsbzcV2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGsbzcV2.jpg&h=5260d2cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3ZAGPo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3ZAGPo.jpg&h=3bd55630&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9aa2ee8538e3dfc204320e16f4e435a21bf985e","tid":2054394,"uid":41545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:42:54.000Z","msg":"不如直接認國家洗左班愚民70年腦都係無用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a723a508796724e9f4e79b6b8d047abd70d61a66","tid":2054394,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T06:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://dingyue.ws.126.net/72XWxjvdnWh3F4oZdZe3f=CdJ82M28YH05uHS2Jzpt7o01552962241930compressflag.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F72XWxjvdnWh3F4oZdZe3f%3DCdJ82M28YH05uHS2Jzpt7o01552962241930compressflag.jpg&h=f410bdad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190718/0a52ffb13fb04444b2